"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t5/s5901"},"text":"5 U.S.C. 5901","children":[],"tail":", and the deletion of subsection (d) thereof, reflect the recodification of subsection (d) in "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t5/s5903"},"text":"5 U.S.C. 5903","children":[],"tail":" by section 1(40)(A) of this bill. In the last sentence of subsection (a), the words “When” and “pays” are substituted for “In those instances where” and “makes reimbursement”, respectively."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idb889acb7-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"idb889acb8-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1992—Subsec. (a)(1), (2). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/378"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–378","children":[],"tail":" substituted “5902)” for “5902).”"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1990—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/509/s529/tII/s202/a/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–509, § 529 [title II, § 202(a)(1)]","children":[],"tail":", substituted “such sums as may be necessary to carry out this subchapter.” for “an amount not to exceed $125 multiplied by the number of employees of the agency who are required by regulation or statute to wear a prescribed uniform in the performance of official duties and who are not being furnished with the uniform.”"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (a)(1), (2). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/509/s529/tII/s202/a/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–509, § 529 [title II, § 202(a)(2)]","children":[],"tail":", substituted “$400 a year (or s